Class SBT

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wmich.cs3310.MPeter.hw3.SBT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISBT

    public class SBT
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISBT
    This class stores a size-balanced binary tree (SBT). Methods of findMin, deleteMin, and insert are used to read and alter the tree.
    Author:
    Matthew Peter
